    "502430": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Mutota",
                    "T": "May the skies forever be clear and bright, and may we always be free to spread our wings and soar. For this wish, the Flower-Feather Clan gathers here today."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "War is a heavy burden. And still, we never stopped moving forward."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "Long-awaited peace is now within reach. You have the opportunity to set that future in motion."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "I'll be rooting for you... Oh, and Coya heard about the battle, so she's here, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Coya",
                    "T": "Cheep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "We both had to make a difficult choice about family. But, after our adventure together, we finally let go of our differences, and she came to understand my attachment to human society."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "Within the tribe, I found new sources of love and happiness. Coya told me she would do anything to protect that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "And I would do the same for her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "The same goes for my human family... Chuychu's father and mother."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "Maybe my relationships seem like a mess to you... But, it's okay. I won't let any one of them fall by the wayside."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "I will learn from everything we've been through and rise above the trials of fate to become a better version of myself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's like you're becoming your own \"peacemaker.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "Thank you, but beyond that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "I pledge to be someone you can lean on in all your future endeavors."
                }
            ],
            [
                {
                    "N": "Chasca",
                    "T": "Thank you for everything. I will always be ready to return the favor."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
