    "502425": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Biram",
                    "T": "A revelation came to me in a dream, and I shared it with my tribe — you are the star that will shine through the mist."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Biram",
                    "T": "The spirits bless your journey."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ororon",
                    "T": "From this day forward, plants will sprout because of you, insects will take flight after you, and all will turn to your will."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That seems like overkill..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ororon",
                    "T": "I disagree. The land of Natlan nurtures life, but the Abyss knows only destruction."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Citlali",
                    "T": "Natlan is also a land of memories and legends."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Citlali",
                    "T": "I live longer than humans, and in all that time, I've learned what life and death mean to people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Citlali",
                    "T": "The dead draw solace from the living, and the living push forward in honor of the dead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Citlali",
                    "T": "In life and death, we all leave marks on this world. We cannot let them be reduced to nothing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I feel the same way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's why I am here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Citlali",
                    "T": "Yes... Thank you for joining this fight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Citlali",
                    "T": "I'll wait for your safe return."
                }
            ],
            [
                {
                    "N": "Ororon",
                    "T": "We're all awaiting your safe return."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Citlali",
                    "T": "Thank you for joining this fight."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "502426": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Acatl",
                    "T": "At the end of the earth lies the primal flame. We have come from afar to offer you our land's blessing and the respect of the Collective of Plenty."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "True strength isn't gifted from the heavens. It culminates little by little from everything we do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "Natlan's history goes back thousands of years. Every person who calls this land home — past or present — has a hand in this opportunity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "Just like the Pyro Archon's concept of time — the past, the present, and the future exist at once. This moment is a convergence of all three."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "I have full confidence in the outcome of this battle. Victory will belong to Natlan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You have my word."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Your hard work will not be in vain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "Actually, I also have a more... personal request."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "Once the war is over, come visit us in the Collective of Plenty, okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Acatl",
                    "T": "Haha, that's right! Our tribe can't wait to meet you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "Varesa and I will show you all our customs and fun activities."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "I'll leave you in suspense for now. But, I promise you won't be disappointed!"
                }
            ],
            [
                {
                    "N": "Iansan",
                    "T": "Varesa and I will show you our tribe's customs and fun activities. Don't miss out!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
