    "502409": {
        "Desc": "Explore up ahead",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Hey, Sis! It's been a long time... This form is probably what I look like in your memories, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Actually, we already met in one of your dreams, didn't we? But... You never told anyone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Out of all the awakened souls, I was surprised \"you\" were one of them. After all, it's been five hundred years."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Hehe, yeah. I'm sure my soul has been reborn many times by now. But, that doesn't mean \"Hine\" is gone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "If the past, present, and future exist at once, then it's only fair we get to meet again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "You're right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "It's too bad we don't have more time to talk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Your plan is almost at the final stage, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "I knew it. When you set your mind to something, there's nothing you can't do, no matter how difficult."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "I really wanted to help you in this era, but an ordinary person can't transcend time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Back then, I said I'd come find you one day. But, I failed time and time again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "You didn't fail."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Wait, then, the paper frog I made... You got it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Yes, and your architecture manual, as well. The family you left it with got it to me in one piece."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Haha, I'm so glad! Five hundred years is a long time... I was worried someone might toss it during a move or something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "No, they never forgot their debt to you. I learned a lot about you from them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Sounds like I placed my trust in the right people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Everything I wrote, though... It's probably outdated now, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Yeah, I'd say so."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Oh, well! It's been a long time, and it's not like I was some innovative architect who left my mark on history."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "But, I lived a really happy life. I dedicated my career to helping those without a home..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "I didn't have time for love, or for myself, but I didn't care. There are so many things in this world that deserve to come first — that's what you taught me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "You never took time for yourself either, did you, Sis?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "No, it wasn't necessary. Besides, I made my choice... And now, the end is near — be it the enemy's end, or my own."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "In the end, the method you used to transcend time was much more than a simple paper frog."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "You sent your love across time. So, let me say this, Hine — I will love you forever and always."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Hehe, I know that! Mom, Dad, and I... We feel the same way about you. We're family — that will never change!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Alright, I need to head out. Another hero is waiting for me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "I believe in you, Sis!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "For Natlan!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
