    "502432": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Vichama",
                    "T": "That was amazing... Judging by your clothes, you're not from Natlan, are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mallko",
                    "T": "I've never seen a soul like you in the Night Kingdom."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Guthred."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "Yes... Although, rather than a soul, it would be more accurate to say that I'm a \"story\" created by the people of Natlan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "I was his most trusted second-in-command. Five hundred years ago, we fought against the Abyss together, and I sacrificed myself during battle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "The shamans of the Masters of the Night-Wind recorded my story on a woven scroll. Even now, many in Natlan know my name."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vichama",
                    "T": "So, you're him, but also not him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "That's right. What you see is the \"me\" from the story. I was remembered as a glorious hero, even though the truth is quite the opposite."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "It was in fragmented memories of my life that I finally began to understand the real \"me.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "Unlike my righteous and noble commander, I was obsessive and cruel, an approach I believed to be more efficient. Our differences caused many an argument between us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No wonder you were ready to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...sacrifice Ororon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mallko",
                    "T": "Y—You tried to... sacrifice someone?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "...\"I\" will stop at nothing to protect my commander's interests."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "The most idealistic and righteous among us are the most fragile, so I must protect his edge. A strong hand is required to stand against a strong foe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "That is what \"the glory of Khaenri'ah\" means to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So, you still believe in him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Even though he's a stranger to you now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "I do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "I have my reasons, as do all who believe in something. You will understand that soon enough."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "Due to the limitations of the Ley Lines, we can go no further. The enemy's lair is close at hand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vichama",
                    "T": "But don't worry — all the souls of the Night Kingdom will lend you their aid."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mallko",
                    "T": "You will become the hero of a new era."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "Go now. For Natlan — and for all who lost their lives to the Abyss."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Guthred",
                    "T": "This time, we shall prevail, not for any single nation or faction, but for us all."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
