    "502420": {
        "Desc": "Explore to find a way forward",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(I didn't expect the situation here to be so chaotic... Is it because of the damage to the Ley Lines?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(The road has collapsed, but the structure above seems intact... That looks like the way forward.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Still, how do I get over there?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Huh? That sound, it's—)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "#Hey, {NICKNAME}! It's me! Chuychu!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Need some help? Doctors can be really handy in an emergency, hehe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "With your special powers, you should be able to make it through this place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Go, now. Go!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Huh? What was that? I felt shaking all of a sudden..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Could it be..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That Mavuika's wrapped up everything on her end?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Ooh, I was wondering where she went."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Well, that just means we've got even less time to waste! I never liked causing trouble, and I definitely don't want to be the one who holds up the Pyro Archon's plan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Chuychu..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You went to see Chasca, didn't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "...Yeah."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "I'm really glad she fulfilled her mission. She seemed a lot more... mature than before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "All those years of worrying, but... better late than never, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Anyway, that was enough for me. I won't show up in her dreams anymore."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Back to the natural order of things — worrying is supposed to be the older sister's job."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're really strong, Chuychu."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "Alright, enough about that. All we can do is accept the past and continue to look forward."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "I would say our nation's future is looking very bright."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chuychu",
                    "T": "#Go now, {NICKNAME}."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
