    "502417": {
        "Desc": "Follow the guidance to reach the destination",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Pacal",
                    "T": "You're about to set off, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Pacal",
                    "T": "Your bravery is like an echo through the valley, calling on us to respond in kind. The Children of Echoes offer you our blessing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Everyone is waiting for you back at the Stadium! We'll be cheering the whole time!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xilonen",
                    "T": "The Abyss is powerful, but there's no reason to fear. We've defeated it before, and you can do it again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xilonen",
                    "T": "Oh, and I brought Nepecha with me. She really wanted to see you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nepecha",
                    "T": "#Hello, {M#Mr.}{F#Miss} {NICKNAME} ..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nepecha",
                    "T": "Not too long ago, you and Xilonen saved me, and helped me recover my real name."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nepecha",
                    "T": "And now, you're going somewhere super dangerous in the name of everyone in Natlan..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "#Yeah, {F#s}he's amazing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nepecha",
                    "T": "Xilonen says a name is like a blessing, so I wanna give you my blessing, too."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nepecha",
                    "T": "But, um, I don't know any fancy words, so... Just be safe, and come visit us soon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nepecha",
                    "T": "We can celebrate your birthday next time!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sounds good to me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kachina",
                    "T": "Hehe, then it's a promise!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xilonen",
                    "T": "That's right — a promise to meet again in the future."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xilonen",
                    "T": "Our tribe is always open to you. Whenever you choose to return, we'll welcome you back with a huge feast of barbecue and wine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xilonen",
                    "T": "I have no doubt that victory will be ours."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
